<template>
  <v-navigation-drawer v-model="drawer">
    <v-container class="" style="height: 100%">
      <v-row>
        <v-column class="" style="width: 100%">
          <v-list>
            <v-list-item
              v-for="(item, index) in items"
              :key="index"
              :value="item"
              :to="item.url"
            >
              <v-list-item-title v-text="item.text"></v-list-item-title>
              <template v-slot:prepend>
                <v-icon :icon="item.icon"></v-icon>
              </template>
            </v-list-item>
          </v-list>
          <v-expansion-panels>
            <v-expansion-panel
              v-model="panel"
              title="Users"
            >
              <v-list>
                <v-list-item>lp</v-list-item>
                <v-list-item>lp</v-list-item>
                <v-list-item>lp</v-list-item>
              </v-list>
            </v-expansion-panel>
          </v-expansion-panels>
        </v-column>
      </v-row>
    </v-container>
  </v-navigation-drawer>
</template>
<script>
export default {
  name: "NavDrawer",
  props: {},
  data() {
    return {
      drawer: false,
      panel: false,
      items: [
        { text: "Home", url: "/", icon: "mdi-home-outline" },
        { text: "Settings", url: "settings", icon: "mdi-cog-outline" },
        { text: "About", url: "about", icon: "mdi-information-outline" },
      ],
    };
  },
  methods: {
    openDrawer() {
      this.drawer = !this.drawer;
    },
  },
};
</script>
